 He formed these words silently with his lips many times before he could say them out loud . When he did finally speak them , he said them clearly , though slowly . 
 How did this happen ? WAS IT YOU ? 
 Once again the two men jumped as the old man turned toward her suddenly . But she sat completely still there as he held onto her and only said quietly , Please , gentlemen , don't come near us . Don't speak . Don't move . 
