 Father ! Even to hear that you thought such things about a daughter who never existed hurts me as if I had been the daughter you speak of . 
 You , Lucie ? It is because of the comfort and strength that you have brought me that we can talk about these memories now under the moonlight on our last night together . What did I say just now ? 
 The daughter you had imagined didn't know anything about you and didn't care about you . 
