 I hope that I am that child , father . O my dear father , will you bless me as eagerly tomorrow . 
 Lucie , the reason I remember these troubled times is the same reason I love you tonight more than words can say . I thank God for how happy I am . My thoughts , when they were the most disturbed , never reached the happiness that I have had with you and that we have still ahead . 
